long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
No sign in, no pay, just simply click and save!

Create short link only for yourself, either a deep drive folder or a random page, save a short link with go link plugin.

Simply type `go` and space key, then put in the short link you previously saved.

Features:
- Sync with your google account.
- Add current tab with your preferred go link.

To come:
- Share saved go links with family or friends.
